  "orders": ["F BRE - MAO", "A PAR - PIC", "A MAR - GAS"]
}

Reasoning:
Seize the Atlantic lane to threaten England's Portuguese/Spanish flank (MAO) while pushing Picardy to pressure Belgium and Gascony to contest English SPA—this balances defense against Germany's likely central push and leverages Iberian influence to coax England into cooperation.
